benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: GET /1.0/kb/customFields/search/{searchKey} - Search custom fields

covered: Valid Request and happy path tested (TC01).
Pagination and limit/offset handling across multiple scenarios (TC02, TC07, TC08, TC09, TC28).
Audit parameter support including FULL/MINIMAL/NONE (TC03-05) and combined with pagination (TC28).
Error handling for invalid parameters (TC11-14) and unsupported method (TC30).
Security considerations (XSS/injection) via TC18; Unicode handling (TC27); whitespace edge-case (TC25); boundary length (TC26).
Default values and edge-case scenarios (TC21, TC29).
Stress tests and large datasets coverage (TC19, TC07).
gaps: Rate limiting / throttling tests are missing (e.g., 429 responses).
Caching behavior and headers (ETag, Cache-Control) are not tested.
403 Forbidden scenarios (authenticated but not authorized) are not covered.
500 Internal Server Error scenarios (server/database failure) are not covered.
Additional targeted performance benchmarks beyond the existing stress test could be added.
recommendations: Add rate-limiting tests to verify proper handling of bursts and 429 responses.
Add tests for caching headers and caching behavior (ETag/Cache-Control).
Add 403 Forbidden tests to verify proper error handling for insufficient permissions.
Add 500 Internal Server Error scenario tests to cover server-side failures.
